by 1 for each additional Malice spent on this feature. If an undead 
is reduced to 0 Stamina during this dread march, they don't die 
until the march is resolved.
Spectral Undead and Phasing
All spectral undead have some kind of phasing trait that 
enables them to move through creatures and objects at their 
usual speed. However, they can't end this movement inside 
a creature or object while in combat. Outside of combat, a 
spectral undead might hide themself inside a statue, painting, 
or other object. But when battle begins, they can't remain 
within or fall back to that cover to prevent being attacked.

