Vampires and Sunlight
In some stories, vampires act only in the dark of night, since 
direct sunlight sears their skin. Learning about a vampire's 
weaknesses before delving into their domain can also make 
for a great adventure or downtime project. To explore sunlight 
rules with vampires, you can give them the following traits.
Creature of the Night
